fields.rule_full:
function init (args)
        local needs = {}
        needs["http.request_line"] = tostring(true)
        return needs
    end

    function match(args)
        a = tostring(args["http.request_line"])
        if #a > 0 then
            if a:find("^POST%s+/.*%.php%s+HTTP/1.0$") then
                return 1
            end
        end

        return 0
    end

    return 0
